OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a "much-
OL,7,Floved" court bailiff who died after
OL,8,Fbeing attacked whilst at work in
OL,9,FCounty Durham.
OL,11,FPolice were called to reports that a
OL,12,Fman had been assaulted in Dent Street
OL,13,Fin Shildon, on Tuesday 10 March,
OL,14,Fshortly after 1pm.
OL,16,FThe victim, former police officer Jeff
OL,17,FBlair, 55, sustained serious injuries
OL,18,Fand died after being taken to James
OL,19,FCook University Hospital in
OL,20,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
