FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1773668260
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,FDurham Police have said a man has been
OL,7,Fcharged with murder in connection to
OL,8,Fthe incident.
OL,10,FRobert Davies, 49, has been charged
OL,11,Fwith murder, possession of an
OL,12,Foffensive weapon, and affray. He has
OL,13,Fbeen remanded in custody ahead of an
OL,14,Fappearance at Peterlee Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt on Friday 13 March.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
