PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1773668260
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Sharon
OL,7,FAlderson, who is leading the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said: "This has been a
OL,9,Fdeeply upsetting incident which has
OL,10,Fcaused a great deal of shock to the
OL,11,Flocal community.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts are with Jeff's family
OL,14,Fand all those who knew and loved him
OL,15,Fat this difficult time.
OL,26,@pD@VOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1773668260
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,F"We will continue to have a police
OL,7,Fpresence at the scene, and I'd like to
OL,8,Fthank the public and nearby residents
OL,9,Ffor their patience, understanding, and
OL,10,Fco-operation while we work to
OL,11,Festablish exactly what has happened."
OL,13,FPolice asked anyone with information
OL,14,Fto call Durham Constabulary on 101,
OL,15,Fquoting incident reference 209 of
OL,16,FMarch 10.
OL,18,FMr Blair worked as a police officer
OL,19,Ffor Durham Constabulary for 22 years
OL,20,Fbefore retiring in 2017 prior to
OL,21,Fbecoming a bailiff.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
