PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1773668260
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Blair's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "Jeff was a much-loved son,
OL,8,Fbrother, father, partner, uncle and
OL,9,Fgood friend to many.
OL,11,F"His ability to apply humour and
OL,12,Flaughter to any situation and lighten
OL,13,Fthe mood will be irreplaceable to our
OL,14,Ffamily."
OL,16,FDarlington Storm Basketball Club said
OL,17,FMr Blair was a "former player, coach
OL,18,Fand committee member".
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUvD@HO]yD@POUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
