PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1773668260
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,FIn a tribute shared on social media,
OL,7,Fthe club said: "Our thoughts and
OL,8,Fprayers are with his family at this
OL,9,Fvery traumatic and troublesome time."
OL,11,FA colleague at a court in the North
OL,12,FEast of England, who asked not to be
OL,13,Fnamed, said of Mr Blair: "He was a
OL,14,Flovely guy and an absolute gentleman."
OL,16,FAn HM Courts and Tribunals Service
OL,17,Fspokesperson said: "Our thoughts and
OL,18,Fcondolences are with Jeff Blair's
OL,19,Ffamily, friends and those who worked
OL,20,Fwith him."
OL,26,@oD@POUqD@eO]uD@ZOUvD@fO]yD@TOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
