OL,3,CTributes paid to 'much-loved' court
OL,4,Cbailiff who died after assault at work
OL,6,FIt is understood the courts service
OL,7,Fwill review what happened and whether
OL,8,Ffurther action is needed to protect
OL,9,Fbailiffs in the course of their work.
OL,11,FAccording to the Government website,
OL,12,Fcourt bailiffs or enforcement agents
OL,13,Fcan visit people's homes if debts are
OL,14,Foutstanding, such as council tax
OL,15,Fbills, fines or court judgments.
OL,17,FA bailiff may be used to serve court
OL,18,Fdocuments or give notices and summons.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
